EXTRACTED VALUE: MotoGP 07 is not a vast improvement over last year's game, but it is a good solid experience nonetheless.
Fans of the genre will probably get their rocks off, but casual gamers will find it a big tease.
A little more challenge to the puzzles and a little less emphasis on realism in the physics department would have helped make RoboBlitz a better game.
Spider-Man 3 certainly has its enjoyable moments, but camera issues and repetitive combat keep it from reaching its full potential.
Shadowrun is a good online FPS.
Some great concepts and even an original feature or two. This is a solid RPG, but ultimately not one you'll remember six months down the track.
